                Method
                Endpoint
                Description

                GET
                /api/users
                Retrieve a list of all users with optional filtering parameters
                Active
                100/hour
            
            
                POST
                /api/users
                Create a new user account with validation
                Active
                10/hour
            
            
                PUT
                /api/users/{id}
                Update an existing user's information completely
                Beta
                50/hour
            
            
                PATCH
                /api/users/{id}/profile
                Partially update user profile data
                Deprecated
                25/hour
            
            
                DELETE
                /api/users/{id}
                Permanently delete a user account and all associated data
                Active
                5/hour
            
        
    
    
    Rate limits are enforced per authenticated user. Status indicators show the current stability of each endpoint.
